#. Id: 52565-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Swamper cook
#: 52565-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "*Sigh* Everyone underrates the cook. But you know what, without a good cook you'll be shitting sideways for the rest of your days. Part of a swordsman's training, a scientists research... part of it all is good food! How can you improve without the fuel to nourish the mind and body?!"
msgstr "*嘆氣*每個人都低估了廚師。但是你知道嗎，如果沒有一個好廚師，你會在剩下的日子裡側身。作為劍客訓練的一部分，科學家研究......其中的一部分都是美食！如果沒有燃料來滋養身心，你怎麼能改善？！"

#. Id: 52661-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (52565-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Swamper cook
#: 52661-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "So, there you go. Hire me."
msgstr "所以，你去吧。僱用我。"

#. Id: 52662-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.1
#. -- Parent line: 1 (52661-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Swamper cook
#: 52662-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "Maybe, how much?"
msgstr "也許，多少錢？"

#. Id: 52662-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.2
#. -- Parent line: 1 (52661-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Swamper cook
#. Id: 52668-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.1
#. -- Parent line: 0 (52561-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Hire Cook
#: 52662-Dialogue.mod:2 52668-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "Depends, what's your price?"
msgstr "取決於，你的價格是多少？"

